<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink138-kilavi">
        talaimakaṉ vāyilpeṟṟup pukuntatu aṟiyātu vanta pāṇaṟkut talaimakaḷ nakaiyāṭic colliyatu. </p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Said with a laugh by the heroine to the bard who came without knowing of the hero’s entry/arrival, having been granted entry.
 </p>
 </div> 
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink138">
<l>paṇpilai maṉṟa pāṇa vivvū</l>
<l>raṉpila kaṭiya kaḻaṟi</l>
<l>meṉpulak koṇkaṉait tārā tōyē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>You have no character, oh bard: </l>
    <l>Thundering [at me with] loveleless [words], </l>
      <l>You did not give [back] to this town</l>
      <l>The man from the maritime tract with soft soil.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
